title: FOUNDERS' DAY Attractions
body_text: You can't have Founders' Day without a First Lady and this historic clash will soon set many ECD records.. it's husband vs. wife, Kevin vs. Leah on February 19! Plus, how about a secondary attraction The Writer has always wanted to host!! Who will win the mystery cash prize in this ECD-first?
